{
  "id": "RAW_c003b558",
  "title": "万相发布「角色扮演」，千问率先接入",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247509994&idx=1&sn=48b6f9d5f83a2b6a066b84f0028718fb",
  "date": "2025-12-17 12:56:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:12px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:24px;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:8px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频生成有个老难题：</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(198, 110, 73);font-weight: bold;\">角色一致性</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个问题，之前一直没被很好的解决，</span><span leaf=\"\">直到 Sora 2 推出了&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-weight:400;font-size:14.4px;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:4px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:3px 5px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-feature-settings:normal;opacity:0.9;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">Cameo</span><span leaf=\"\">，才算是有个被认可的东西</span></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如下面这个，Sam 禅位 CEO 给我</span></p>\n   <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div></div>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">12月16日，阿里发布万相 2.6，支持了</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-weight:400;font-size:14.4px;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:4px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:3px 5px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-feature-settings:normal;opacity:0.9;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">角色扮演</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">从模型的角度，是目前最接近 Cameo 的</span></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(198, 110, 73);font-weight: bold;\">同一时间，千问集成了万相</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin-left:8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100026345\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7151932239280042\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3778\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.5em;margin-left: auto;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYqL04s2dykaibOQBtFw0hHuKvjI0XoyRRPbx6gJyYleh7GQLLEmxV9DqgIrcoeHbRGVKV3pV8Msic3A/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"298\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"390\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b510cdd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYqL04s2dykaibOQBtFw0hHuKvjI0XoyRRPbx6gJyYleh7GQLLEmxV9DqgIrcoeHbRGVKV3pV8Msic3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">社区上，出现了很多「角色扮演」的成片</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <h3 style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:18px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px !important;margin-left:8px !important;border-width:0px 0px 1px 4px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid solid dashed;margin-bottom:24px !important;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">角色扮演</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><code style=\"padding:3px 5px;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-size:14.4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:4px;font-feature-settings:normal;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">万相2.6</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;把这个能力叫「角色扮演」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">123</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin-left:8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"></figure>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">给模型一段参考视频，它能提取里面的角色外观、音色、动作特征，然后按照你的描述生成新视频</span></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">角色在新视频里保持一致</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时支持多人合拍：两个角色在同一个视频里互动，各自保持一致</span></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还支持智能分镜：输入一段描述，自动拆成多个镜头，镜头之间角色、场景、氛围保持统一</span></p>\n   <p style=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.9;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">角色扮演：潮酷女在咖啡厅说「周末不用上班真舒服」</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 